<div style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h1 style="color: #111; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">You're approved</h1>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Hi <%= @user.name.presence || 'there' %>!</p>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Your provider account for <strong><%= @business_name %></strong> has been approved. Your business is now visible to customers on OllaZen.</p>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Log in to your dashboard to manage bookings, services, and your profile.</p>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">— The OllaZen team</p>
</div>
